                <b>
                    NIGERIAN MIDSTREAM AND DOWNSTREAM PETROLEUM REGULATORY AUTHORITY
                </b>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: -1em;">
                <h5>Plot 1012 Cadastral Zone A00, Sani Abacha Way, Central Business District, Abuja, FCT, Nigeria.</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="width: 100%; text-align: center; position: absolute; top: 50%; margin-top: -400px;">
            <img src="~/assets/coat-of-arm.jpg" style="width: 920px; opacity: 0.1; margin-left: -5em;;" />
